  56,35,"'ina 'anshana nisa' 'ahl aljanat nshat ghyr alnash'at alty kanat fi aldnya, nshat kamilat la tuqbal alfna', fajaealnahuna abkarana, mthbbat 'iilaa azwajhn, fi snn wahdt, khlqnahn li'ashab alymyn"
